<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BLUR VINTAGE â˜…</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .hero-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .hero-image {
            width: 800px; 
            height: 400px; 
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: center;
        }

        .brand-text {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .about-section {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .about-section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .contact-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }

        .contact-section h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .contact-section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .contact-link {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: underline;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-link:hover {
            color: #666;
        }

        /* For smaller screens */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .hero-image {
                width: 90%;
                height: 300px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .hero-image {
                width: 95%;
                height: 250px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header partial will be included here -->
    <%-include('../../views/partials/user/header.ejs')%>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <img src="/images/about.jpeg" alt="Blur Vintage Fashion" class="hero-image">
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about-section">
        <h1 class="brand-text">BLUR VINTAGE</h1>
        <p>Founded in Kerala, India in 2017, Blur Vintage has emerged as one of the world's leading clothing brands. Following our centenary, Blur Village continues to forge ahead, redefining clothing while celebrating creativity, craftsmanship, and innovation.</p>
        
        <p>As part of the global clothing group, Blur Vintage manages renowned Houses in fashion, jewelry, and eyewear, maintaining our commitment to excellence and authentic style.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section class="contact-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h3>May We Help You?</h3>
            <p>Discover everything you need to know about the Blur Vintage universe with a Client Advisor.</p>
            <p><a href="#" class="contact-link">Contact Blur Vintage Client Services</a></p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer partial will be included here -->
    <%-include('../../views/partials/user/footer.ejs')%>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>